{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: GRONCKLE'S POV - the teens targets become blurry and scrambled.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: It's working.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: GOBBER (CONT'D)
{DIALOGUE}: All dragons have a limited number of shots.
{DIALOGUE}: How many does a Gronckle have?
{CHARACTER_NAME}: SNOTLOUT
{DIALOGUE}: Five!
{CHARACTER_NAME}: FISHLEGS
{DIALOGUE}: No, six.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: GOBBER
{DIALOGUE}: Correct, six.
