{DIALOGUE}: Hiccup squeezes through and enters the cove.
{DIALOGUE}: A BEAT, then Hiccup hears a SNORT from behind him.
{DIALOGUE}: Hiccup turns to see the Night Fury, crouched on a rock like a stealthy panther.
{DIALOGUE}: It descends, approaching him... ready to pounce.
{DIALOGUE}: Hiccup swallows his fear and offers the fish.
{DIALOGUE}: Doing so reveals the dagger at his waist.
{DIALOGUE}: The dragon sees it and hisses.
{DIALOGUE}: Hiccup reaches for it, eliciting a growl.
{DIALOGUE}: He pauses, carefully lifts it by the handle, and tosses it away.
{DIALOGUE}: The dragon calms.
{DIALOGUE}: As it approaches the fish, Hiccup notices that it's missing teeth.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: HICCUP
{DIALOGUE}: Huh.
{DIALOGUE}: Toothless.
{DIALOGUE}: I could've sworn you had... A set of razor sharp teeth emerge from its gums to grab the fish.
{DIALOGUE}: Toothless snatches and gnashes it up, swallowing it.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: "Dragon" DeBlois/Sanders Final Draft (Rev.19) 02-13-2010 38.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: HICCUP (CONT'D)
{DIALOGUE}: ... teeth.
{DIALOGUE}: The teeth retract again.
{DIALOGUE}: Toothless presses closer with an expectant look.
{DIALOGUE}: Hiccup retreats nervously.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: HICCUP (CONT'D)
{DIALOGUE}: Uh, no.
{DIALOGUE}: No, I don't have any more.
{DIALOGUE}: The Fury backs Hiccup against a rock, placing himself the same position as before.
{DIALOGUE}: The dragon closes in over him, staring blankly.
{DIALOGUE}: A tense moment passes... then Toothless regurgitates a chunk of fish onto Hiccup's lap.
{DIALOGUE}: They exchange stares.
{DIALOGUE}: Hiccup realizes what Toothless wants him to do.
{DIALOGUE}: Hiccup crouches slowly and squeamishly picks it up.
{DIALOGUE}: The dragon waits expectantly.
{DIALOGUE}: Hiccup gags and gnaws off a bite of the slimy fish.
{DIALOGUE}: He forces a smile.
{DIALOGUE}: Toothless mimics him.
{DIALOGUE}: Amazed, Hiccup sits up and tries to touch him.
{DIALOGUE}: Toothless HISSES and flaps off to a crash on the other side of the cove.
{DIALOGUE}: He BLASTS the mossy ground to a red-hot temperature... and curls up on it like a giant dog.
{DIALOGUE}: He turns to find Hiccup seated beside him.
{DIALOGUE}: Toothless tolerates his persistent presence... until Hiccup tries to touch his damaged tail.
{DIALOGUE}: Toothless SNAPS at him.
{DIALOGUE}: Hiccup takes the hint and leaves.
{META_DATA}: DISSOLVE TO:
{SCENE_BOUNDARY}: EXT. COVE - LATER
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: It's MAGIC HOUR.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Toothless wakes, hanging upside down from a tree.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: He spots Hiccup sitting on the other side of the cove.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Sketching in the sand.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: CLOSE ON a sketch of Toothless.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Hiccup draws with a stick, minding his own business.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Toothless appears behind him, watching carefully.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Aware of his presence, Hiccup continues, trying not to scare him off.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Toothless walks off.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: A moment later, he reappears with an entire sapling, drawing lines in the sand.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: He rushes here and there, making haphazard lines in every direction.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Finally, Toothless drops the tree and inspects his work.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: He seems pleased.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: "Dragon" DeBlois/Sanders Final Draft (Rev.19) 02-13-2010 39.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Hiccup stands and takes in the sprawling scribble, amazed by it.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: He accidentally steps onto one of the lines, eliciting an instant growl from Toothless.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: He steps on it again.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Toothless growls again.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Realizing how sensitive he is, Hiccup steps carefully between each line, turning round and round until he unwittingly bumps into Toothless.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Toothless snorts.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Once again, they're face to face.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Hiccup slowly extends his hand.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Toothless hesitates.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Hiccup turns his head away and closes his eyes.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: To his amazement, Toothless bridges the gap and presses his muzzle against Hiccup's hand.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: In a flash, the dragon is gone, leaving Hiccup astounded.
{SCENE_BOUNDARY}: EXT. VILLAGE - NIGHT
