{DIALOGUE}: As a result, Hiccup is suddenly PULLED TIGHT against the window shutters.
{DIALOGUE}: He STRIKES A POSE to compensate... then gets PULLED THROUGH the shutters.
{DIALOGUE}: They snap back in Astrid's face.
{DIALOGUE}: Astrid reopens them and finds nothing but an empty stall.
{DIALOGUE}: In the distance, Toothless and Hiccup slip off unseen.
{SCENE_BOUNDARY}: EXT. DOCKS - DAWN
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: A lone, battered ship is pulled into a slip, overloaded with equally battered-looking men.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: They disembark to a crowd of onlookers, looking like a team of hometown heroes who just had their butts kicked.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Gobber hobbles through the MUMBLING crowd to find Stoick -- last to disembark and glowering with battered pride.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: "Dragon" DeBlois/Sanders Final Draft (Rev.19) 02-13-2010 51.
