{SCENE_BOUNDARY}: EXT. SKY - AFTERNOON
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Toothless and Hiccup soar through a perfect blue sky.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Billowing clouds rise like mountains.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: The ground seems miles below them.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: HICCUP
