{DIALOGUE}: They careen past the wooded cliff and directly into a treacherous slalom course of jutting sea stacks.
{DIALOGUE}: Hiccup pulls the cheat sheet from his teeth and attempts to check positions.
{DIALOGUE}: It flaps violently in the turbulence, making it impossible.
{DIALOGUE}: With no time to think, Hiccup throws it away and steers Toothless' tail on instinct... with perfect intuition.
{DIALOGUE}: Together, they manage a tight, hair-rasing series of split- second turns, making it to the open water, unscathed.
{DIALOGUE}: Hiccup takes a breath and glances back at the death-defying obstacle course, now safely behind them.
