{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Below them, Berk's torches flicker in the inky darkness.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: The new perspective is breathtaking.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Astrid tucks her arms into Hiccup's vest, burying her chin into his shoulder.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: The moment is not lost on either of them.
