{DIALOGUE}: Dragons of all breeds lay about, nested in hordes.
{DIALOGUE}: The arriving dragons fly in, dropping the fish and game into a central pit, glowing red and shrouded in mist.
{DIALOGUE}: Hiccup is amazed.
