{DIALOGUE}: With a little Hiccup flare thrown in.
{DIALOGUE}: Think it'll do?
{CHARACTER_NAME}: HICCUP
{META_DATA}: (bittersweet, coming to
{CHARACTER_NAME}: TERMS)
{DIALOGUE}: I might make a few tweaks.
{DIALOGUE}: Astrid appears and jabs Hiccup in the arm.
{DIALOGUE}: Hiccup recoils with a grumble.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: ASTRID
{DIALOGUE}: That's for scaring me.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: HICCUP
{META_DATA}: (PROTESTING)
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: What, is it always going to be this way?
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Cause I..
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: She grabs him aggressively... then kisses him.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Hoots and hollers follow.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: HICCUP (CONT'D)
{DIALOGUE}: ... could get used to it.
{DIALOGUE}: Gobber presents Hiccup with a rebuilt saddle, rigging, and tail.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: GOBBER
{DIALOGUE}: Welcome home.
{DIALOGUE}: Suddenly, Toothless pounces on the crowd, crushing several unsuspecting Vikings under his weight.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: VIKING
{DIALOGUE}: Night Fury, get down!
{DIALOGUE}: Toothless eyes the new tail excitedly, tongue wagging.
{DIALOGUE}: Amidst the groans and grumbles, Hiccup and Astrid exchange a sheepish grin.
{META_DATA}: CLOSE ON
{CHARACTER_NAME}: CLOSE ON
{DIALOGUE}: Hiccup's prosthetic foot, snapping into the modified stirrup.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: "Dragon" DeBlois/Sanders Final Draft (Rev.19) 02-13-2010 105.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: The two pieces click together, forming a single shape.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Astride Toothless, he's whole again.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: He rotates the pedal.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: The new tail opens.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Bright red with a skull and Viking horns emblazoned on it.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Hiccup approves.
{META_DATA}: CUT BACK TO REVEAL...
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Hiccup and Toothless, saddled up and ready to fly.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Astrid backs her Nadder into position.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: HICCUP
{META_DATA}: (TO TOOTHLESS)
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: You ready?
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Toothless SNORTS an excited 'yes!'
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: From his mount, Hiccup looks out over the changed world.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: HICCUP (V.O.) (CONT'D)
{DIALOGUE}: This... is Berk.
{META_DATA}: (BEAT)
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: It snows nine months of the year... and hails the other three.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: They LEAP into the bright blue sky, together as one.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Astrid follows, giving chase.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: HICCUP (CONT'D)
{DIALOGUE}: Any food that grows here is tough and tasteless.
{DIALOGUE}: The people that grow here are even more so.
{DIALOGUE}: Hiccup and Astrid race their dragons through the village -- under eaves, over rooftops, down cliff-sides, and between ship masts.
{DIALOGUE}: It's a high energy, romantic dance of sorts.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: HICCUP (V.O.) (CONT'D)
{DIALOGUE}: The only upsides are the pets.
{DIALOGUE}: While other places have...ponies or parrots, we have... Their fellow recruits join them as they take to the open sky, rocketing far above the village.
{DIALOGUE}: The Northern sky swirls with blazing, multicolored dragons.
{DIALOGUE}: Hiccup and Toothless break from the pack, spinning into the blinding sun.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: HICCUP (V.O.) (CONT'D)
{META_DATA}: (PROUDLY)
{DIALOGUE}: ... dragons.
{META_DATA}: FADE TO WHITE
